&lt;p&gt;Here, the distance between A&amp;nbsp;and F is 5 m.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;5 m&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;दी गयी जानकारी के अनुसार दूरी और दिशा आरेख:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Mrunal_Engineering_24.11.2022_D25.2.png&quot; style=&quot; width: 412px; height: 318px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;यहाँ, A और F के बीच की दूरी 5 मीटर है।&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;अत:, सही उत्तर&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&amp;quot;5 मीटर&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;है।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Here, we use the table given below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage651e6f7f61ca949327e84aee.png&quot; /&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Logic: Addition and subtraction of &amp;#39;1&amp;#39; alternatively.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;HALLUCINATED&amp;#39; is written as &amp;#39;IZMKVBJMBSFC&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/04/F1_SSC_%20PRIYA_17_4_24_D45.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

